WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.933 --> 00:00:03.233
Why is there only one creek?

2
00:00:03.466 --> 00:00:04.633
I don't know either.

3
00:00:07.366 --> 00:00:09.166
How do you explain Chenxi?

4
00:00:09.166 --> 00:00:10.300
I don't know.

5
00:00:10.766 --> 00:00:13.666
I don't know another thing about Xiaoxi

6
00:00:14.266 --> 00:00:15.466
On you

7
00:00:15.466 --> 00:00:18.766
You don't know what Huo Zeyuan is, do you?

8
00:00:18.766 --> 00:00:20.166
You were in a car accident

9
00:00:20.200 --> 00:00:22.433
It wasn't Chenxi who donated your kidney at all

10
00:00:22.500 --> 00:00:23.500
It was a stream.

11
00:00:26.166 --> 00:00:28.366
How could you possibly say that?

12
00:00:28.766 --> 00:00:31.166
I only owe the old days a rest

13
00:00:31.166 --> 00:00:33.866
Yes, he was already pregnant with your child

14
00:00:33.866 --> 00:00:35.900
He risked his life to donate to you

15
00:00:36.266 --> 00:00:38.766
You still listen to the words of this woman in the early morning

16
00:00:38.766 --> 00:00:41.166
Huo Zeyuan, you're sorry Xiaoxi

17
00:00:41.366 --> 00:00:43.700
Early morning Xi turned out to be you

18
00:00:43.700 --> 00:00:46.500
Why did you lie to me? Why?

